data.description: A true Tomball Treasure!  an exquisite home with  great features, family open to dining, eat at kitchen bar, bay window breakfast room, updated vinyl plank flooring in family, living and formal dining areas. Wooden stairs with attractive wrought iron railing, built in book case, lots of closets for storage, recessed ceilings, double stainless steel oven, white indoor window shutters and much more. The master bath is huge with a gorgeous updated freestanding white tub with gold accented faucet. The bedrooms are spacious and the master has W/D connections in the closet. all appliances including washers and dryers to remain with home. There is a cool and refreshing salt water pool nestled in the backyard oasis ready for all your home entertaining events, fountain will remain. All information is deemed correct but not guaranteed buyer is responsible to certify information provided. Please note there are cameras that may record with audio and video at all times.
